      "content": "the meeting's not really an option, the decision's already finalized and the deployment is scheduled for tonight. the whole point of the patch is to move away from these long \"nuanced\" discussions because they're too unpredictable. the new rules are non-negotiable, so there's not much to debate at this point.",
